/TD><TD COLSPAN=\\\"5\\\"><TABLE CELLSPACING=\\\"0\\\" CELLPADDING=\\\"0\\\" LANG=\\\"en-US\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><TR><TD style=\\\"WIDTH:56.78mm;min-width: 56.78mm;HEIGHT:3.97mm;\\\" class=\\\"a51l\\\">Author: Dillon Schoolcraft</TD></TR></TABLE></TD><TD ROWSPAN=\\\"4\\\" COLSPAN=\\\"2\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD style=\\\"HEIGHT:4.06mm;WIDTH:0.00mm\\\"></TD><TD COLSPAN=\\\"20\\\"></TD></TR><TR VALIGN=\\\"top\\\"><TD style=\\\"HEIGHT:4.06mm;WIDTH:0.00mm\\\"></TD><TD></TD><TD COLSPAN=\\\"5\\\"><TABLE CELLSPACING=\\\"0\\\" CELLPADDING=\\\"0\\\" LANG=\\\"en-US\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><TR><TD style=\\\"WIDTH:42.67mm;min-width: 42.67mm;HEIGHT:4.06mm;\\\" class=\\\"a24\\\">Notice Text</TD></TR></TABLE></TD><TD ROWSPAN=\\\"2\\\" COLSPAN=\\\"14\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD style=\\\"HEIGHT:1.78mm;WIDTH:0.00mm\\\"></TD><TD COLSPAN=\\\"6\\\"></TD></TR><TR VALIGN=\\\"top\\\"><TD style=\\\"HEIGHT:6.35mm;WIDTH:0.00mm\\\"></TD><TD></TD><TD COLSPAN=\\\"21\\\"><TABLE CELLSPACING=\\\"0\\\" CELLPADDING=\\\"0\\\" LANG=\\\"en-US\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><TR><TD style=\\\"WIDTH:195.11mm;min-width: 195.11mm;HEIGHT:6.35mm;\\\" class=\\\"a54 r8\\\"><DIV style=\\\"overflow-x:hidden;WIDTH:193.70mm;\\\"><DIV style=\\\"margin-top:10pt;padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Columbia Gas Transmission, LLC (TCO) notifies customers of upcoming maintenance activities on Line H&#160;scheduled to begin on Wednesday, April 1, 2026. As a result, the following meters will be reduced to zero total capacity effective Timely Cycle for Gas Day April 1, 2026, and continuing until the work is complete:</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">821917 – A&amp;W-Gandee</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">840254 – Vandalia</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">842446 – Spencer H Line Sales</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Based on current scheduled volumes, the anticipated impact to firm service is less than 2,000 Dth/day.&#160;</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Additionally, during the first phase of the outage (tentatively scheduled April 1-16, 2026), meter 833237 (behind MLI CNR18) will be required to&#160;physically shut in. Therefore, effective Timely Cycle for Gas Day April 1, 2026, CNR18 will be reduced to zero non-firm.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">TCO encourages customers to monitor the Construction and Maintenance Schedule and the Daily Capacity Posting for any non-firm adjustments related to this maintenance.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Reservation charge credits (RCCs) will be determined per the process set forth in the General Terms and Conditions, Section 38 of TCO’s FERC Gas Tariff (“Tariff”).&#160;However, TCO will only issue RCCs if TCO is unable to schedule or deliver primary firm nominated capacity as a result of the outage.&#160;In the event RCCs are issued as set forth in the Tariff, shippers will receive RCCs based on its 7-day average usage quantity less any scheduled quantities on the contract. By means of this notice, TCO is establishing which specific Gas Days will be included when determining a shipper’s 7-day average usage quantity pursuant to the provisions in the Tariff.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';font-size:11.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Please contact your Customer Services Representative with any questions.</span></DIV></DIV></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></TD><TD WIDTH=\\\"100%\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"0\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH=\\\"0\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"100%\\\"></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></DIV></body></html>\"}],\"temperature\":0.1,\"max_tokens\":2000,\"response_format\":{\"type\":\"json_object\"}},\"headers\":{\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\",\"api-key\":\"AwX1mym8WNOwDFipRpDFxrz1bvaIAZJFkHH126iCClxlMtQOH5GUJQQJ99CDACHYHv6XJ3w3AAAAACOGUqcL\"}},\"outputs\":{\"statusCode\":400,\"headers\":{\"x-ms-rai-invoked\":\"true\",\"X-Request-ID\":\"57609d86-c201-4f7d-b45b-9bb1655bc855\",\"apim-request-id\":\"a25c3c8b-39a4-4c18-860f-fb7093296311\",\"Strict-Transport-Security\":\"max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload\",\"x-ms-client-request-id\":\"fe4a63f0-7880-40ff-ad21-208fee000d0b\",\"x-ms-deployment-name\":\"gpt-5.2\",\"X-Content-Type-Options\":\"nosniff\",\"x-ms-region\":\"East US 2\",\"Date\":\"Mon, 20 Apr 2026 17:14:14 GMT\",\"Content-Length\":\"245\",\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"},\"body\":{\"error\":{\"message\":\"Unsupported parameter: 'max_tokens' is not supported with this model. Use 'max_completion_tokens' instead.\",\"type\":\"invalid_request_error\",\"param\":\"max_tokens\",\"code\":\"unsupported_parameter\"}}},\"startTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:14:14.9495272Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:14:15.3815911Z\",\"trackingId\":\"2824a033-b5a1-48fe-8761-a040cda1fbf7\",\"clientTrackingId\":\"08584249018052146792210398495CU00\",\"code\":\"BadRequest\",\"status\":\"Failed\"},{\"name\":\"Parse_Foundry_Response\",\"startTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:14:15.3953758Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-2